What is it?\
\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\'97\
\
This code solves for the stationary equilibrium of the agent\'92s maximization problem using the Overlapping Generations (OLG) Model. In essence the program solves for the vector of asset demands and consumption values that maximizes the agent\'92s utility, as well as the optimal asset price. The hope is that this program may act as one component of a larger model of the welfare implications of climate change, as outlined in the 2009 paper by Andrew Leach.\
